[
    {
        "text": "When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.10919540229885058,
        "end_progress": 0.10919540229885058
    },
    {
        "text": "You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.10919540229885058,
        "end_progress": 0.10919540229885058
    },
    {
        "text": "On the screen I see myself as a doctor who works in remote areas to save lives.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 69.0,
        "start_progress": 0.109717868338558,
        "end_progress": 0.15203761755485892
    },
    {
        "text": "One day I am called to a village to treat a patient.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 69.0,
        "end_time": 81.0,
        "start_progress": 0.15256008359456635,
        "end_progress": 0.17972831765935215
    },
    {
        "text": "The patient is very sick and needs medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 81.0,
        "end_time": 106.0,
        "start_progress": 0.18025078369905956,
        "end_progress": 0.203239289446186
    },
    {
        "text": "I have no medicine with me, but I try to make the patient comfortable and wait for him to get well.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 106.0,
        "end_time": 118.0,
        "start_progress": 0.20376175548589343,
        "end_progress": 0.2554858934169279
    },
    {
        "text": "The next day I went to a different village to find the right medicine for the sick patient.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 118.0,
        "end_time": 159.0,
        "start_progress": 0.2560083594566353,
        "end_progress": 0.30355276907001044
    },
    {
        "text": "I leave the patient behind and continue my journey.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 159.0,
        "end_time": 180.0,
        "start_progress": 0.30407523510971785,
        "end_progress": 0.33072100313479624
    },
    {
        "text": "I found the medicine but it was very expensive.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 180.0,
        "end_time": 196.0,
        "start_progress": 0.33124346917450365,
        "end_progress": 0.3557993730407524
    },
    {
        "text": "I was sad, thinking that the patient will not be able to afford it.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 196.0,
        "end_time": 208.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3563218390804598,
        "end_progress": 0.39132706374085685
    },
    {
        "text": "So I used my own money to pay for the medicine to save the man.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 208.0,
        "end_time": 225.0,
        "start_progress": 0.39184952978056425,
        "end_progress": 0.42476489028213166
    },
    {
        "text": "I returned to the village and gave the medicine to the patient.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 225.0,
        "end_time": 234.0,
        "start_progress": 0.42528735632183906,
        "end_progress": 0.45820271682340646
    },
    {
        "text": "After one day the man started regaining his health.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 234.0,
        "end_time": 264.0,
        "start_progress": 0.4587251828631139,
        "end_progress": 0.48537095088819227
    },
    {
        "text": "The patient was very thankful and promised to pay me back.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 264.0,
        "end_time": 276.0,
        "start_progress": 0.48589341692789967,
        "end_progress": 0.51619644723093
    },
    {
        "text": "I told him it was not necessary since I knew it would be very hard for him to pay me.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 276.0,
        "end_time": 301.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5167189132706375,
        "end_progress": 0.5611285266457681
    },
    {
        "text": "I left the village and continued on with my journey.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 301.0,
        "end_time": 319.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5616509926854755,
        "end_progress": 0.5888192267502612
    },
    {
        "text": "The next day I was called to another village for work.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 319.0,
        "end_time": 351.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5893416927899686,
        "end_progress": 0.6175548589341693
    },
    {
        "text": "This time it was a sick woman who needed medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 351.0,
        "end_time": 369.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6180773249738767,
        "end_progress": 0.6442006269592476
    },
    {
        "text": "She had been sick for a whole week.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 369.0,
        "end_time": 378.0,
        "start_progress": 0.644723092998955,
        "end_progress": 0.6630094043887147
    },
    {
        "text": "I was still thinking about the patient from the previous day.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 378.0,
        "end_time": 388.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6635318704284221,
        "end_progress": 0.6954022988505747
    },
    {
        "text": "\"What if she also can't afford medicine?\", I wondered.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 388.0,
        "end_time": 423.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6959247648902821,
        "end_progress": 0.7241379310344828
    },
    {
        "text": "But I decided to treat the woman anyway.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 423.0,
        "end_time": 437.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7246603970741902,
        "end_progress": 0.745559038662487
    },
    {
        "text": "I treated her for a few days, and the woman started feeling better.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 437.0,
        "end_time": 450.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7460815047021944,
        "end_progress": 0.7810867293625914
    },
    {
        "text": "She paid me for the medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 450.0,
        "end_time": 469.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7816091954022989,
        "end_progress": 0.796760710553814
    },
    {
        "text": "As it turns out she was very wealthy and could afford the medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 469.0,
        "end_time": 491.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7972831765935214,
        "end_progress": 0.8322884012539185
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I heard what you did,\" she said, referring to paying for the other patient's medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 491.0,
        "end_time": 522.0,
        "start_progress": 0.832810867293626,
        "end_progress": 0.8782654127481714
    },
    {
        "text": "And she slipped a diamond into his hand.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 522.0,
        "end_time": 549.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8787878787878788,
        "end_progress": 0.8996865203761756
    },
    {
        "text": "\"You can keep this as a reward.\" And then she left.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 549.0,
        "end_time": 565.0,
        "start_progress": 0.900208986415883,
        "end_progress": 0.9268547544409613
    },
    {
        "text": "As I watched this on the screen I was so amazed.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 565.0,
        "end_time": 583.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9273772204806687,
        "end_progress": 0.9535005224660397
    },
    {
        "text": "I guess in another life I finally learned that kindness can pay off in unexpected ways.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 583.0,
        "end_time": 615.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9540229885057471,
        "end_progress": 0.9994775339602926
    }
]